  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127650/extras/5cdccb14195830f49269c4da12878543.avif?t=1743641851\" width=600 height=100 /></span>It is a co-op fps game with the theme of supernatural events and suspense, where you can play with your friends with a minimum of 3, do roles and missions. You can have a realistic gaming experience with features such as proximity chat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127650/extras/434d7f8f756ac866c914e3585609ce89.avif?t=1743641851\" width=600 height=100 /></span>You've traveled with your team to an abandoned town to investigate a surreal event, but one of you has been cursed and wants to secretly eliminate you before you complete the ritual to be saved. Be cautious, survive, collect the necessary materials and break the town's curse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127650/extras/3ef45336dee10d6b70fded9866b6dc58.avif?t=1743641851\" width=600 height=100 /></span>He might be watching you, maybe you are in danger, maybe you are the danger... Keep your eyes open and play your role well.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127650/extras/5cdccb14195830f49269c4da12878543.avif?t=1743641851\" width=600 height=100 /></span>It is a co-op fps game with the theme of supernatural events and suspense, where you can play with your friends with a minimum of 3, do roles and missions. You can have a realistic gaming experience with features such as proximity chat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127650/extras/434d7f8f756ac866c914e3585609ce89.avif?t=1743641851\" width=600 height=100 /></span>You've traveled with your team to an abandoned town to investigate a surreal event, but one of you has been cursed and wants to secretly eliminate you before you complete the ritual to be saved. Be cautious, survive, collect the necessary materials and break the town's curse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127650/extras/3ef45336dee10d6b70fded9866b6dc58.avif?t=1743641851\" width=600 height=100 /></span>He might be watching you, maybe you are in danger, maybe you are the danger... Keep your eyes open and play your role well.</p>",
